m','','','Gardening','g.s@agg.it'),(41,'Pack of 3 large 272L garden waste bags','Height 76 cm, Diameter 67 cm','','Gardening','g.s@agg.it'),(42,'Fire Pit Steel Heater Grill Camping Bowl BBQ','Large folding Steel Fire Pit Garden Patio Camping Heater BBQ. This beautifully crafted traditional steel fire pit is sure to be the perfect heating option or BBQ for your garden patio, terrace or when your camping.','','Gardening','g.s@agg.it'),(43,'Percussion Musical Instruments Set for Kids, 25 Pcs','Kids can have fun finding rhythm and melody in everyday life. Musical Instruments Set can enrich their language, social development, cognition, attention span, mathematical, motor and self-regulation skills.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(44,'Adjustable Black Orchestral Musical Sheet Holder Tripod Stand','Is perfect for use within home, stage or studio. Made from durable metal with a non-reflective black finish. The stand is Height and Angle Adjustable, and ideal for several pages of Sheet Music.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(45,'Martin Smith W-100 Acoustic Guitar','The preferred choice for thousands of guitarists. Designed especially for students, this full size steel strung guitar comes complete with a strap, spare strings, plectrums and free online lessons. The body is perfectly contoured for a comfortable playing position.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(46,'Full Size Electric Guitar Superkit','Is the ideal musical package for children and adults who want to start learning to play right away. This standard size electric guitar can play a variety of distinct notes, making it great for musicians who want to try anything from light rock to heavy metal.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(47,'Guitar Basics','It is full of effective graphics, songs and clapping games, jokes that work and well-known movie and rock tunes (some using tab). The book, which is attractively illustrated and moves with ease through the lessons, getting to grips with rhythm and then simple notation, building to the beginnings of repertoire, featuring original and selected tunes.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(48,'54-Key Portable Digital Piano Keyboard with Music Stand','The 54-Key Digital Piano Keyboard is perfect for aspiring pianists of all ages. This compact, portable, and high quality keyboard has built-in stereo speakers and a large, easy-to-read LCD screen, which serves as a great teaching tool.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(49,'Yamaha P-45 Digital Piano - Black','The P-45 from Yamaha, one of the worlds leading musical instrument manufacturer, is the enhanced model in the P-Series range with a compact and portable design which makes it useful on the road, in the home or in the classroom.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(50,'Piano Time 1: Bk. 1','The highly popular Piano Time series has undergone a full facelift. Free supplementary material for the series is also included.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(51,'Windsor Full Size 4/4 Violin','The Windsor violin is the perfect instrument for students. With a spruce top, ebony coloured tuning pegs and fingerboard and fine tuning adjusters, it produces a bright tone and comes complete with a wood/horsehair bow.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(52,'Odyssey OFL100 Flute Outfit - Black','At Odyssey, we recognise the significant contribution that an instrument makes to the willingness of a student to persevere, practice, pursue the process of learning to control and master the instrument, enjoy making music and progress.','','Music','g.s@agg.it'),(53,'Tool Kit Precision Tools 82 Piece DIY Home Household Tool Set',' This 82-piece homeowner\'s set includes all the hand tools needed which completed the basic DIY projects around the home. And all tools are packed neatly in a blow molded case for easy tool storage. This tool kit was tested against industry standards for hardness, torque, finish and usability.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(54,'Makita B-43044 Drill and Bit Set, Blue/Black','The Makita B-43044 66 Piece Drill and Bit Set offers a comprehensive selection for the serious tradesman and offers great value for money. This bit set comes in a Makpac type 1 case which offers additional storage underneath the top tray as well as being able to be stacked onto other Makita Makpac cases.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(55,'Unassembled 3D printer DIY Kit high quality excellent','Pro B i3 3D printer is designed and manufactured by Shenzhen Geeetech Co., Ltd, an international company whose commitment is to provide high quality 3D printer for this world. This printer is very popular all around the world, applied to wide fields such as household, product prototype design.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(56,'3D Printing Pen, Aerb Intelligent 3D Pen with LCD screen','Creativity abounds and the imagination is sparked. Great idea for toy! Aerb Intelligent 3D Printing Pen is the Newest Version 3D Pen in the current market. With Aerb 3d printing pen, you can bring your creative thoughts into a real object.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(57,'328 Feet Natural Durable Jute Twine Rope Decocord','1 reel of ecological handmade cable, decorative cord.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(58,'Metallic Pens, Pack of 8 High Quality Pens','Papermania\'s metallic pens for an shimmery finish. Bullet tipped for doodling, adding borders, patterns and craft projects. Available in pack of eight.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(59,'Modelcraft Precision Craft Knife Set','Precision Craft Knife Set With Different Shapes to Better Achieve What You Want to Create (16pcs)','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(60,'Scola Artmix Ready Mix Coloured Paint - 12','Artmix is possibly the most widely used painting medium in primary school classrooms. It is part of the Scolaquip Eco range, using natural thickeners and being wheat and gluten free.','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(61,'Acrylic paint 24 Set For Paper,...','The Finest Quality Acrylic Paints for ALL of Your Artistic Needs!','','DIY & Painting','g.s@agg.it'),(62,'25 pcs Set, 30x50cm Canvas, Ac